    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Any type of building, complex, room, or other space where ropes are made. For rope-making facilities housed in long, narrow buildings or spaces and serving the marine and seafaring industries, use "ropewalks."</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
